description: Canadian Air Force - Never Say Die - The Canadian Air Force Survival Manual (1982) (pdf) - roflcopter2110 https://worldimages.gallery/image/jusX Genre: Air Travel, Hiking & Camping, Instructional, Adventure Publisher: Paladin Press Language: English ISBN-10: 0873641124 ISBN-13: 978-0873641128 Format: PDF This Canadian Air Force Manual is a detailed study of what to do if you find yourself in a survive-or-die situation. Techniques on how to survive in almost any terrain from desert to frozen arctic tundra are presented. But unlike other survival manuals, these techniques include valuable data on how to combat fear, pain and panic - and win the struggle against the elements
